Assuming there are a total of 200 results: 

{noformat}
{recently-updated} 
{noformat}

Will produce a list of 15 (this is the current default page size) results followed by a "more" link. Clicking the link will output the next page of results inline, preserving the user's context. 

This will work for the default theme (which is the 'concise' theme) and the social theme. These are accessible by specifying the macro parameter {{theme=concise}} and {{theme=social}} respectively. 

Extra pages of results will be served inline up until a total of 100 results has been displayed (so 2 pages of 50 or 10 pages of 10). This limit will be enforced for performance reasons.

